OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W"  #! "E`
OL,5,BMICROBRITS: A Tapestry Of The British  
OL,6,BGaming Industry by S.L.Perrin.         
OL,8,B81681 words, 141 pages, (almost) forty 
OL,9,Byears of gaming history, 15 studios, 12
OL,10,Bmonths of research, 1 book.            
OL,12,EMICROBRITSBis a look at the history of 
OL,13,BtheEBritish gaming industryBthrough the
OL,14,Bvery companies who shaped it.          
OL,16,BBeginning withEImagine SoftwareBin 1982
OL,17,Band covering almost four decades of    
OL,18,BBritish gaming, ending withERockstar   
OL,19,ENorthBin 2019.                         
