OL,5,BMICROBRITS by S.L.Perrin               
OL,7,BImagine, Ocean, Psygnosis, U.S. Gold,  
OL,8,BUltimate Play The Game, Rare, Bitmap   
OL,9,BBrothers, Gremlin Graphics, Sensible   
OL,10,BSoftware, Team17, DMA Design, and Rock-
OL,11,Bstar North areEall covered.            
OL,13,BLooking atEeach company,Bthe people    
OL,14,Bbehind it, and some ofEthe gamesBthey  
OL,15,Bproduced.                              
OL,17,BThe book is designed so you can jump in
OL,18,Banywhere, but if read cover to cover an
OL,19,Binteresting tapestry is revealed.      
