OL,4,E`````````````````````````````W"  #! "E`
OL,5,BMICROBRITS by S.L.Perrin               
OL,7,BYou can play a good game of six degrees
OL,8,Bof separation with this book. Yarns of 
OL,9,BinterestingEpartnerships,Bback-stabbing
OL,10,Bbuy outs, bitterErivalries,Bsurprising 
OL,11,Binterweaving tales and fascinating tit-
OL,12,Bbits along the way.                    
OL,14,BMICROBRITS is a journey through almost 
OL,15,Efour decadesBof British gaming and how 
OL,16,Bsome of the biggest names in the indus-
OL,17,Btry, some still working today began... 
OL,18,Bas well as some pretty spectacular     
OL,19,Bfailures.                              
