OL,5,BMICROBRITS by S.L.Perrin               
OL,7,BWhen you're done reading this fascinat-
OL,8,Bing story of how theEBritish gaming    
OL,9,Eindustry was born,Bthere's a nice bonus
OL,10,Bat the end.                            
OL,12,BA special three part look at "the most 
OL,13,Bimportant British game designer ever". 
OL,14,BAn in-depth look at the career ofEPeter
OL,15,EDouglas Molyneux.                      
OL,17,BThe author takes you through the story 
OL,18,Bfrom baked bean salesman, to co-founder
OL,19,BofEBullfrog,BviaELionhead,BtoE22Cans.  
